rdt.tree

Class MultilabelChainTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • rdt.tree.Tree
      • rdt.tree.MultilabelChainTree

  • public class MultilabelChainTree
extends Tree
    Class which represents a MultilabelChainTree. This tree differs from the normal tree only in the way that it contains information about the label-splitters (splitters which test on a label-attribute) and information about the attribute-ids of the splitters which have been used for the last prediction (This information can be used to speed up the prediction-process of the multilabel-chain algorithm).
    Author:
    MK
